      "text": "The summer's end",
      "start": 44.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 48.97999954223633,
      "text": "I see you walking",
      "start": 46.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 52.619998931884766,
      "text": "And I know there'll be more I'm afraid of",
      "start": 48.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 53.86000061035156,
      "text": "The summer's end",
      "start": 52.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 56.86000061035156,
      "text": "I'll see you again",
      "start": 54.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 63.2400016784668,
      "text": "I'll see you standing there looking just as beautiful, my friend",
      "start": 56.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 68.30000305175781,
      "text": "I know this can't be the end",
